name: Vacuum (PaperBagOfficial)
description:
Best played in fullscreen mode. If you have a broken spawn reload the game.

Move through a randomly generated dungeon as a vacuum cleaner destroying dust bunnies. Not strong enough to defeat an enemy? Increase your damage  at the cost of a small sum of your health. The same applies in vice versa. All music created by https://youtube.com/c/teknoaxe
